          <title>Apple's Macs Drive PC Sales Rebound, Canalys Data Shows</title>
          <description><![CDATA[Apple's Mac sales account for a significant chunk of the global PC recovery sales, according to Canalys data. The company's desktop and notebook shipments increased 22.1%, giving it a 10.4% share of the global PC industry.]]></description>
